{"article_id":"Daeuwdl6hUarXyaG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump at a Kansas rally celebrated the confirmation of Brett Kavanaugh to the Supreme Court ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"condemning Democrats for what he called a `` shameless campaign of political and personal destruction '' against his nominee .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"To cheers of supporters at the Kansas Expocentre in Topeka , Trump declared","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"it an `` historic night , ''","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"not long after signing the paperwork","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to make Kavanaugh 's status official .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"`` I stand before you today on the heels of a tremendous victory for our nation , ''","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"he said to roars ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"thanking Republican senators","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"for refusing to back down `` in the face of the Democrats ' shameless campaign of political and personal destruction . ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Kavanaugh was sworn in as a justice Saturday evening in Washington after an extraordinarily fraught nomination","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that sparked angry protests , nail-biting votes and a national reckoning about sexual assault allegations and who should be believed .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Kavanaugh staunchly denied the allegations ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"but nearly all Senate Democrats voted against his confirmation .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The final vote took place Saturday afternoon","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"as the president was flying to Kansas aboard Air Force One ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and he invited traveling reporters to his private office","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"to watch the climactic roll call ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"which was interrupted several times by protesters in the Senate galleries","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"before Capitol Police removed them .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"When it was official ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Trump delivered a double thumbs-up from his desk .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Several aides applauded .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"`` Very , very good , ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"`` Very happy about it .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Great decision .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"I very much appreciate those 50 great votes","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"he 's going to go down as a totally brilliant Supreme Court Justice for many years . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Trump , throughout the day , insisted","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Kavanagh would not be tainted by the sexual assault allegations from Christine Blasey Ford and others","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that nearly tanked his nomination .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"he was `` 100 percent '' certain","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Kavanaugh was innocent .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` I have no doubt , ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"telling reporters","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that he had chosen Kavanaugh , in part ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"because `` there 's nobody with a squeaky-clean past like Brett Kavanaugh . ''","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"the FBI had done seven background investigations","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"and argued","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"had there been an issue ,","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"it would have surfaced sooner .","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"`` If there was even a scintilla of something wrong","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"- he was a very big judge for many years","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"on what they call the second highest court -","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"that would have come out loud and clear , ''","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Throughout the day , Trump also kept his focus on the opposition ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Kavanaugh had withstood a `` horrible , horrible attack ''","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that `` nobody should have to go through . ''","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"He continued lashing out at Democrats","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"when he rallied supporters in Topeka ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"telling them","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"`` radical Democrats '' have become `` an angry , left-wing mob '' and `` too dangerous and too extreme","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to govern . ''","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"He urged Kansas voters to send Republicans to Congress .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"`` You do n't hand matches to an arsonist","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and you do n't give power to an angry left-wing mob .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"And that 's what they 've become , ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Kavanaugh 's nomination sparked protest across the Capitol ,","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"which continued Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"When the vote was over ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"hundreds of protesters massed on the Supreme Court steps ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"chanting ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"`` We believe survivors . ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Asked by reporters aboard Air Force One","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"what message he had for women across the country","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"who feel","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the nomination sends a message","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that their allegations of sexual assault are n't believed ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Trump disagreed with the premise ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"women `` were outraged at what happened to Brett Kavanaugh ''","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and `` were in many ways stronger than the men in his favor . '' `` We have a lot of women","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that are extremely happy","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"- a tremendous number -","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"because they 're thinking of their sons ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"they 're thinking of their husbands and their brothers and their uncles and others","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and women are ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"I think ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"extremely happy , ''","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"he added .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Trump has repeatedly sided with men","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"accused of sexual misconduct","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"and has warned of the dangers","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"false accusations pose to men","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"even though research has shown false accusations to be extremely rare .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Pointing to television footage of protesters outside the Capitol ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"their numbers paled in comparison to the thousands of supporters","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"awaiting him in Kansas .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"`` The crowd in front of the U.S. Supreme Court is tiny ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"looks like about 200 people","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"( & most are onlookers ) -","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that would n't even fill the first couple of rows of our Kansas Rally , or any of our Rallies for that matter ! ''","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Trump also revealed","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that he believed","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"a widely criticized rally speech","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"in which he mocked Ford 's Senate testimony","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"had been a turning point for the nomination ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"changing the momentum in his favor .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that the Mississippi speech had great impact , ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"calling it `` a very important thing . ''","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"He later told Fox News host Jeanine Pirro in an interview from his limousine","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"once he made the comments ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"`` it started to sail through . ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Advisers and Senate leaders had urged Trump not to attack Ford publicly ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"worried","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"such a move would anger on-the-fence senators .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"But Trump went after her anyway ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"mocking her testimony and gaps in her memory","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"as a rally crowd laughed","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"and cheered .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"`` I thought","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"I had to even the playing field , ''","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Trump was in Kansas","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"to campaign for Kris Kobach , secretary of state and the Republican nominee for governor , and Steve Watkins , the GOP nominee in the 2nd Congressional District of eastern Kansas .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Retiring Republican Rep. Lynn Jenkins holds the seat ,","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"and Democrats hope to flip it .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Both joined him on stage at the Expocentre","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"to speak .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"Trump has been holding rallies across the country","depth":3},{"id":135,"text":"as he tries to boost Republican turnout in November 's midterm elections ,","depth":4},{"id":136,"text":"which will determine","depth":5},{"id":137,"text":"which party will control the House and Senate during the second half of Trump 's term .","depth":5},{"id":138,"text":"He said Saturday","depth":4},{"id":139,"text":"he thinks","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"Republicans `` are going to do incredibly well '' in the elections after Kavanaugh 's confirmation .","depth":5},{"id":141,"text":"`` I think","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"we have a momentum","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"that has n't been seen in years , ''","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":289,"left":278,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":210,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":196,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":196,"left":154,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":146,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":149,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":157,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":155,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":194,"left":172,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":165,"right":171,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":162,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":158,"right":161,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":14,"right":15,"re